### SSE Progress Tracking Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000

### 0. Login to get JWT Token
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 1. Start Screening to get Progress ID
POST http://localhost:3000/api/prep-closing/screening
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6MSwidXNlcm5hbWUiOiJhZG1pbiIsInJvbGUiOiJhZG1pbiIsImlhdCI6MTc1ODA5ODQ0MiwiZXhwIjoxNzU4MTg0ODQyfQ.5pQMcr019dCoXQkFowIPo-q-rDCY8XdHuy3eiWeO0zU

