###
### Instructions for Testing SSE:
###
### 1. First run the screening endpoint (#1) to start a screening process
### 2. Copy the progressId from the response
### 3. Replace "PROGRESS_ID_HERE" in endpoint #3 with the actual progress ID
### 4. Run the SSE endpoint (#3) - you should see real-time progress updates
### 
### Expected SSE Response Format:
### data: {"type":"connected","progressId":"your-progress-id"}
### 
### data: {"type":"progress","data":{"status":"running","currentStep":1,"totalSteps":5,"message":"Processing..."},"timestamp":"2024-01-17T10:30:00.000Z"}
### 
### data: {"type":"finished","status":"completed"}
###
### Note: SSE connections will automatically close when screening is completed or failed